platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: What child could resist the idea of ​​making a race by embodying Thomas the little train, taking Garfield's picture and decorating his nails with Hello Kitty? Not ours. They marvel at the Montreal app Budge World and its selection of fun activities featuring their favourite characters.
